title: Pro Line® Series Automatic Toasters | KitchenAid
description: The KitchenAid Pro Line® series 2- and 4-Slice Automatic Toasters feature an automatic lift, seven shade settings, a keep-warm function and much more. They deliver a premium performance with a timeless design inspired by the iconic Stand Mixer.

asset.author: KitchenAid
asset.hookText: The KitchenAid® Pro Line® series 2- and 4-Slice Automatic Toasters feature an automatic lift, seven shade settings, a keep-warm function and much more. They deliver a premium performance with a timeless design inspired by the iconic Stand Mixer. Go to http://www.kitchenaid.com/countertop-appliances/pro-line/ for more countertop appliance information and culinary inspiration.

transcripts: Engineer for performance, the KitchenAid pro line series delivers exceptional culinary results. Introducing the pro line 2 and 4 slice automatic toasters, developed for the discerning gourmet. The two and four slice toasters deliver outstanding performance with the timeless design inspired by the iconic KitchenAid stand mixer. Simply insert your bread and watch it lower automatically with your choice of seven shades settings. On busy mornings the auto keep warm initiate soon after the toasting cycle is complete or select a little longer when toasting is complete but not quite as dark as your preferred. Premium performance, bringing unmatched luxury to your kitchen. The KitchenAid pro line series.
